Title: <tt>df</tt>: Show volume name in service output
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1631524879
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

It is now possible to see the volume name in the output of a Filesystem service
for Linux and Windows hosts.

To configure this set the option <tt>Show volume name in service output</tt> in Setup -> Services ->
Service monitoring rules -> Filesystems (used space and growth) to enabled.
